sequenceDiagram
    participant ADM as Admin/Auditor
    participant API as API Gateway
    participant MD as Metadata Registry
    participant EXP as Export Service
    participant ST as Secure Storage
    participant NT as Notification Service

    ADM->>API: Request compliance evidence pack
    API->>MD: Gather lineage + audit logs
    MD->>EXP: Provide compiled metadata + profiling context history
    EXP->>ST: Store generated evidence bundle
    EXP->>MD: Record export metadata
    NT->>ADM: Send download link/confirmation
    ADM->>ST: Retrieve evidence package
    ST->>MD: Log access event
